{"data":[{"date":"09:11 16/06","title":"Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 vi\u00ean s\u1edf thu\u1ebf v\u1ee5 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo gian l\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011-2014, ng\u00f4i sao kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>14,7 tri\u1ec7u euro</strong>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00ec gian l\u1eadn trong thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, khi d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty ma \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, thu th\u1eadp b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng. Nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span> di\u1ec5n ra, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1edd El Mundo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed h\u1ea7u t\u00f2a, khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i <strong>t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 18,8 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn\" title=\"BDN Ronaldo lap cu dup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <strong>CR7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n t\u00f9 2 n\u0103m. </strong>Th\u00f4ng tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean vi ph\u1ea1m, Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo. Theo Lu\u1eadt, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 n\u0103m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh b\u1ed3i ho\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chi ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u00ea chu\u1ea9n, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo 21 th\u00e1ng, do h\u00e0nh vi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf <strong>4,1 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a CR7, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tr\u1ea1nh&rdquo; v\u1edbi Lionel Messi tr\u00ean &ldquo;m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span><br>\r\nRonaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3643","checkdouble":"188610"},{"date":"09:29 16/06","title":"M.U tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n De Gea th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nDe Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngay sau khi Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o David De Gea. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-180-188491.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Becker</span> &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a AS Roma \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Real mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd l\u00e2u, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c M.U v\u00e0 David De Gea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao De Gea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 350 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Edwin-van-der-Sar-phat-bieu-ve-David-de-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. De Gea l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong c\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Man United l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0y. Cristiano \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng, l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a HLV, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t La Roja h\u1ed7n mang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3642","checkdouble":"188612"},{"date":"08:12 16/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a 17h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-thanh-hoa-17h00-ngay-166-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a 17h00 ng\u00e0y 166 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a 17h00 ng\u00e0y 166 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/xsktct-flcth.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs Thanh H\u00f3a: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">XSKT.CT \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecf t\u00fai 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7y \u0111\u00e2y. Nguy\u00ean do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu d\u1ea7n khi c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c l\u00e0 do m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Patiyo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0 \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00f2i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u1eefu D\u0169ng do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0 cam k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a XSKT.CT \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ti\u1ebfp FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y cho \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Omar do ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ee5\u00a0 \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n XSKT.CT nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao. N\u1ebfu ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u1ea5y, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nXSKT.CT: V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i, T\u00f9ng Qu\u1ed1c, Ho\u00e0ng Vissai, T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n, Anh Tu\u1ea5n, Quang T\u00ecnh, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ed9c, Trung Anh, \u00dat C\u01b0\u1eddng, Wander, Patiyo.<br>\r\nFLC Thanh H\u00f3a: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc, \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, Xu\u00e2n\u00a0 H\u01b0ng, Xu\u00e2n T\u00f9ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Hi\u1ebfu, Quang Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Th\u1ebf D\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Nam, Ofere. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3641","checkdouble":"188606"},{"date":"19:12 15/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/6: K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-156-ke-hoach-100-trieu-bang-cua-mu-bi-pha-san.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/6.\r\n</h2><h2>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 156 K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Bale c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 156 K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Bale c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/Mourinho-cheo-keo-Gareth-Bale-voi-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ESPN, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid. HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Bale c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 sao Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Barca \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Gazzetta dello Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri thay Conte v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Real Madrd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Keylor Navas\" title=\"thu mon Keylor Navas\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Keylor Navas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Corriere dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin, Napoli \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Le10Sport, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Van der Sar b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap De Gea tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Edwin van der Sar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Rugani tr\u1ecb&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-2112-Arsenal-chi-dam-tranh-hang-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Calciomercato.com \u0111\u01b0a tin, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gotze mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Premier League</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dortmund, Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, b\u00e1o c\u00e1o Mirror. Arsenal, Everton, West Ham, Leicester v\u00e0 Newcastle \u0111\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Gotze, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3640","checkdouble":"188576"},{"date":"20:26 15/06","title":"Barca chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/1/barca-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-sao-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Andres Iniesta, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/1/barca-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-sao-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ilkay Gundogan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd theo Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Man City b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Man City ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 2017, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Gundogan, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd t\u00e1i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Gundogan r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gundogan v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gundogan\" title=\"Gundogan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/toa-sang-truoc-basel-gundogan-duoc-pep-khen-ngoi-het-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Gundogan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Gundogan. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Fernandinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Fred v\u00e0o tay M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef Gundogan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Man xanh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Gundogan, Barca c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm Christian Eriksen ho\u1eb7c Miralem Pjanic n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, song \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3639","checkdouble":"188578"},{"date":"18:55 15/06","title":"Van der Sar b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap De Gea tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/van-der-sar-bay-cach-giup-de-gea-tro-thanh-thu-mon-so-1-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Edwin van der Sar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David de Gea \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Edwin van der Sar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Edwin van der Sar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Edwin-van-der-Sar-phat-bieu-ve-David-de-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u G\u0103ng tay V\u00e0ng \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.\u00a0Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-du-dinh-mua-de-gea-voi-gia-100-trieu-euro-180-184490.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua De Gea thay Navas</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef De Gea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Van der Sar c\u00f3 l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn De Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Edwin van der Sar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon De Gea gianh Gang tay vang\" title=\"thu mon De Gea gianh Gang tay vang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/11/de-gea-chua-nghi-toi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van der Sar c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn De Gea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn Buffon th\u00ec s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. De Gea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, De Gea v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00e9t l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, De Gea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3638","checkdouble":"188572"},{"date":"01:00 16/06","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/granit-xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Granit Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal. Ch\u00ednh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng qua trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xhaka n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGranit Xhaka chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1eeb Borussia Monchengladbach m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 Premier League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Xhaka c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf c\u1ea3 38 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League bao g\u1ed3m 37 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 1 t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Granit Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Granit Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/9/Granit-Xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Arsenal-den-nam-2023-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Xhaka ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Granit Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal. Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng theo gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m t\u1edbi 2023. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00e0o c\u00e1c Gunners. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Xhaka. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Arsenal\u201d, Xhaka n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. \u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery m\u1eebng khi Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u00f9a t\u1edbi 2018/19, Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Unai Emery. \u00d4ng l\u00ean thay Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Xhaka.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Granit Xhaka\" title=\"tien ve Granit Xhaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/granit-xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Granit Xhaka gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi Xhaka \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d, Emery n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb n\u00ean c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXhaka hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK World Cup 2018. Anh d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Brazil \u0111\u00eam 17/6 t\u1edbi.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span><br>\r\n<span>Gi\u1eefa l\u00fac World Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1nh chi\u1ebfm th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-them-world-cup-arsenal-don-hang-loat-tin-mung-ve-chuyen-nhuong-172-188407.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-them-world-cup-arsenal-don-hang-loat-tin-mung-ve-chuyen-nhuong-172-188407.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup, Arsenal \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Tranh th\u1ee7 k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb di\u1ec5n ra, HLV Unai Emery v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u201cc\u00e0n qu\u00e9t\u201d phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3637","checkdouble":"188587"},{"date":"15:02 15/06","title":"Ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i Nga \"ve v\u00e3n\" quanh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/chan-dai-nga-ve-van-quanh-khach-san-tuyen-anh-dong-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd The Sun cho hay, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&ldquo;Chuy\u1ec7n \u1ea5y&rdquo; \u1edf World Cup l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn, r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ra &ldquo;lu\u1eadt&rdquo; th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. X\u01b0a nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 v\u1ed1n tho\u00e1ng trong vi\u1ec7c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n kh\u1eaft khe h\u01a1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e1i Nga ve v\u00e3n, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e1i Nga ve v\u00e3n, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh5-1529034466-815-width660height450.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Anh lu\u00f4n tho\u00e1ng khi d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi ri\u00eang \u0110T Anh, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 &ldquo;truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng&rdquo; cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111i theo, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn. N\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. HLV Gareth Southgate cho d\u00e0n WAGs Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga c\u1ed5 v\u0169, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf chung kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh khi t\u1edbi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 4 sao ForRestMix \u1edf ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 St Petersburg, Nga. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng theo t\u1edd The Sun, con g\u00e1i \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 St Petersburg r\u1ea5t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n Anh qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Theo \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 Tinder, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u00ednh 10km c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh2-1529034511-501-width660height719.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zhanna, 26 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebfn r\u0169</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh1-1529034466-334-width660height625.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p Alexis, 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n &quot;t\u00e2m s\u1ef1&quot; v\u00e0 &quot;l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n&quot; v\u1edbi sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng 21 tu\u1ed5i Alexis chia s\u1ebb \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm &quot;m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup k\u1ebft th\u00fac&quot;. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p 26 tu\u1ed5i Zhanna khoe \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1edbt tha v\u1edbi v\u00e1y tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. Nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i \u0111ang ra s\u1ee9c &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; d\u00e0n sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 HLV Southgate c\u00f3 c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c h\u00fat l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00f4 g\u00e1i St Petersburg c\u1ef1c k\u00ec xinh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0103n ch\u01a1i, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed y\u00ean b\u1ec1 gia th\u1ea5t v\u1ee3 con \u0111\u1ec1 hu\u1ec1. Vi\u1ec7c HLV Southgate kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5m xxx c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y x\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3636","checkdouble":"188554"},{"date":"16:54 15/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n PVF, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/AZ4A9834.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n b\u1ed5 \u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V-League v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t th\u00ec trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 mang theo 25 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u1eeba qua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t do m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec QG nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0110T U20 VN tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u\u00a0 th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 16/6 \u0111\u1ebfn 25/6 t\u1edbi. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 17/6, 20/6 v\u00e0 23/6 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande (B) v\u00e0 CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand FC \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi 14/7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danh sach U19 Viet Nam\" title=\"Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/DS-U19-tap-huan-TQ.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 World Cup</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3635","checkdouble":"188565"},{"date":"17:30 15/06","title":"Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-sap-phai-nhan-an-phat-nang-vi-loi-danh-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF sau h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</h2><h2>Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/a_hoang_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u khi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Douglas sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 gay g\u1eaft tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat th\u1ebb cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, VFF \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Theo tin t\u1eeb ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft chi\u1ec1u nay 15/6 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Rosa Taudin Douglas. N\u1ebfu x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi phi th\u1ec3 thao, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c g\u1eedi sang Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda BTC, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sai, Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd x\u1eed l\u00fd. CLB kh\u00f4ng bao che\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Omar hay Oseni \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng khi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e0 n\u0103ng V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3634","checkdouble":"188571"},{"date":"15:52 15/06","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Porto","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/arsenal-va-chelsea-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-porto.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Vi\u1ec7c Marcos Alonso \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Barca theo \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto thay Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto thay Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Chelsea-muon-mua-Alex-Telles-cua-Porto-thay-Marcos-Alonso-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Alex Telles</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues nh\u1eafm Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo Mirror, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-phuong-an-b-vu-sandro-172-163178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles</span> c\u1ee7a Porto \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992. The Kop mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Alberto Moreno \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Porto.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlex Sandro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t B\u0110N m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 13 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u0110N. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Porto \u0111\u00f2i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Telles v\u1edbi Porto c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Telles r\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Porto chi ban Alex Telles voi gia 35 trieu bang\" title=\"Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/arsenal-va-chelsea-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-porto.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, song Chelsea hay Liverpool v\u1eabn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, song b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Porto.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3633","checkdouble":"188556"},{"date":"16:18 15/06","title":"NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal t\u1eebng h\u1ecfi mua Golovin v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0, h\u1ecd \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eebng h\u1ecfi mua Golovin v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Nga, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Golovin khi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn th\u1ed5n th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi ra \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb CSKA Moscow kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-15-trieu-bang-mua-sao-tuyen-nga-172-187521.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Golovin</span>, Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Song Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ngoi Golovin\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nga-vs-Saudi-Arabia-bang-A-World-Cup-2018-Tuyet-voi-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i twitter, \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London k\u00eau g\u1ecdi HLV Emery \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Neil b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Arsenal h\u00e3y k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Golovin\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Ariel Ehsan Reynaldi cho r\u1eb1ng: \u201cGolovin r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNick Name Ahmad Gozali Siahaan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cGolovin r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng, Arsenal n\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIsmail Mostafa: \u201cArsenal h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi mua Golovin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nStar Lord: \u201cGolovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Rosicky ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i Arsenal\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSILVERSURFER: \u201cN\u1ebfu Wilshere ra \u0111i, Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3632","checkdouble":"188557"},{"date":"11:48 15/06","title":"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/ban-than-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-ronaldo-buon-buc.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nuno Gomes - nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf\" l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb Nuno Gomes d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho CLB, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Barcelona l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Xavi, Iniesta hay Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Ronaldo s\u1ebd ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c. BL\u0110 Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho CR7 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn v\u1eady\", Nuno Gomes cho bi\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/1_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Real Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n Real c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Barcelona t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lionel Messi\", c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Ronaldo hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m, thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi Neymar (32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m) v\u00e0 Lionel Messi (40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m). BL\u0110 Real t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng sau n\u00e0y, th\u1ee9 CR7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i c\u1ee5t l\u1ee7n \"gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 13 n\u0103m \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Barcelona, Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u01b0u \u00e1i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 l\u1ea7n. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp, thu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \"El Pulga\" \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i t\u1eeb 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3631","checkdouble":"188545"}]}